    *   [Auth store](https://github.com/pocketbase/js-sdk#auth-store)
        *   [LocalAuthStore (default)](https://github.com/pocketbase/js-sdk#localauthstore-default)
        *   [AsyncAuthStore (_usually used with React Native_)](https://github.com/pocketbase/js-sdk#asyncauthstore)
        *   [Custom auth store](https://github.com/pocketbase/js-sdk#custom-auth-store)
        *   [Common auth store fields and methods](https://github.com/pocketbase/js-sdk#common-auth-store-fields-and-methods)

    *   [Auto cancellation](https://github.com/pocketbase/js-sdk#auto-cancellation)
